-- South African Public Sector Salary Talks to Continue for Next Seven Days
-- Franz Wild
-- 2010-07-30T08:30:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/south-african-public-sector-salary-talks-to-continue-for-next-seven-days.html

          
          
             The South African government and
public sector unions agreed to continue talks for the next seven
days to resolve a wage dispute, according to a statement
distributed to reporters in the capital, Pretoria today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Franz Wild in Johannesburg at 
 fwild@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        